00325         int CountOwnedNow(TechnoTypeClass *Item) {
00326                 int Index = Item->GetArrayIndex();
00327                 int Sum = 0;
00328                 BuildingTypeClass *BT = NULL;
00329                 UnitTypeClass *UT = NULL;
00330                 UnitClass *U = NULL;
00331                 InfantryTypeClass *IT = NULL;
00332 
00333                 switch(Item->WhatAmI()) {
00334                         case abs_BuildingType:
00335                                 Sum = this->OwnedBuildingTypes.GetItemCount(Index);
00336                                 BT = (BuildingTypeClass *)Item;
00337                                 UT = BT->UndeploysInto;
00338                                 if(UT) {
00339                                         Sum += this->OwnedUnitTypes.GetItemCount(UT->GetArrayIndex());
00340                                 }
00341                         break;
00342 
00343                         case abs_UnitType:
00344                                 Sum = this->OwnedUnitTypes.GetItemCount(Index);
00345                                 UT = (UnitTypeClass *)Item;
00346                                 BT = UT->DeploysInto;
00347                                 if(BT) {
00348                                         Sum += this->OwnedBuildingTypes.GetItemCount(BT->GetArrayIndex());
00349                                 }
00350                         break;
00351 
00352                         case abs_InfantryType:
00353                                 Sum = this->OwnedInfantryTypes.GetItemCount(Index);
00354                                 IT = (InfantryTypeClass *)Item;
00355                                 if(IT->VehicleThief) {
00356                                         for(int i = 0; i < UnitClass::Array->Count; ++i) {
00357                                                 U = UnitClass::Array->GetItem(i);
00358                                                 if(U->Owner == this && U->HijackerInfantryType == Index) {
00359                                                         ++Sum;
00360                                                 }
00361                                         }
00362                                 }
00363                         break;
00364 
00365                         case abs_AircraftType:
00366                                 Sum = this->OwnedAircraftTypes.GetItemCount(Index);
00367                         break;
00368 
00369                         default:
00370                                 ;
00371                 }
00372                 return Sum;
00373         }
